{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I mean by that is that, one day they came in, and I think-- I think this is what is shown so very well in because-- except that I don't think-- rightly so, it was not shown in its complete horror.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because what really happened is that the German-- well, I don't know whether they were SS or soldiers or whoever-- took some of the children and absolutely knocked their heads on the walls.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They swung them by the legs and killed them that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a horrible experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw it, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all saw it, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what did I think?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The overwhelming emotion that has probably ruled my life has been fear-- fear of authority and fear in general.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, you know, the overwhelming emotion that I remember was fear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know-- not so much anger, but kind of a questioning, how could anybody do anything like that?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was at the age of 12 that I know that I lost my faith in God, because I knew that no-- I mean, the Jews believed that God-- at least the explanation was-- that the reason things were happening to the Jews because of the sins of our forefathers.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I simply couldn't believe that any god would allow a child to be killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had-- I had my doubts about it, and I have not really resolved them since.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Babies.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we went-- we were transported out of the ghetto and into Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe they took us by trucks-- or we walked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't even remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We might have walked directly from the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
